ed="T" n="0879a01"/><persName key="A013712">釋貞幹</persName>，俗姓<name>武</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000003893">雲中</placeName>人也。神宇高邈，以禪<lb
ed="T" n="0879a02"/>默為務。曳錫踽步<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2154"/>，南訪靈跡，及至<placeName key="PL000000013136">故<anchor xml:id="beg0879sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>障</sic><corr>鄣</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0879sgsz1"/></placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0879a03"/>有<placeName key="PL000000049696">崑山寺</placeName>者，林泉秀茂，則<date from-iso="+0420-07-11" key="j18746541896160" to-iso="+0479-05-29"><name>宋</name></date><ptr target="#n3336"/><persName key="A001800">支曇諦</persName>甞考室<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2155"/><lb
ed="T" n="0879a04"/>于此，味道<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2156"/>崇化二十餘載，基蹠存焉！至<date notBefore-iso="+0424-09-18" key="j18761841886591" notAfter-iso="+0453-03-17"><name>元<lb
ed="T" n="0879a05"/>嘉</name>中</date>創成大伽藍。屬<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>廢教，<ref type="place" target="#PL000000049696">其寺</ref>屏除。<lb
ed="T" n="0879a06"/><persName key="A013712">幹</persName>至止於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000049696">茲</ref>，與<placeName key="PL000000002485">范陽</placeName><persName key="A013713">盧君襲</persName>同興<persName key="A002854">弘覺<roleName>法<lb
ed="T" n="0879a07"/>師</roleName></persName>第二生<ptr target="#n3335"/>名跡。寺成，進士<persName key="A013716">姚扶</persName>有詩。<persName key="A013712">幹</persName>後遊<lb
ed="T" n="0879a08"/>今<placeName key="PL000000012747"><name>秀州</name><name>長水</name></placeName>，見<placeName key="PL000000012759">靈光寺</placeName>，邑民欲樹巨殿<ptr target="#n3337"/>。時<lb
ed="T" n="0879a09"/><persName key="A013713">盧<roleName>令</roleName></persName>移邑字民<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2157"/>，欣然相遇，<persName key="A013712">幹</persName>悉先知。或云<lb
ed="T" n="0879a10"/>得他心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g396"/>、宿命<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2158"/>之明焉！遂請<persName key="A013712">幹</persName>首唱。而惡偃<lb
ed="T" n="0879a11"/>室之囂，寓殿基後，編苫為淺室而居。四方<lb
ed="T" n="0879a12"/>檀信，弗召自臻。又與僧令<persName key="A013715">恭君道</persName>等累歲方<lb
ed="T" n="0879a13"/>成今殿。其最高廣，海內罕比。事畢，挈弊囊，<lb
ed="T" n="0879a14"/>振舊錫歸北，莫知其終。</p>
